          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1698925998946-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> duck leg[s]</strong>, <strong>Chantenay carrots </strong>and <strong>waxy</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Top your potatoes and carrots with the <strong>duck fat </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 30-35 min or until the duck leg[s] is golden and crispy and the potatoes are tender</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
